Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Medical Office Building located in Houston, TX, purpose-built to accommodate easy ingress and egress for patients

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The property is well-located along I-10 East between 610 Loop and Beltway 8.  Its location gives it exposure to an abundance of hospitals and credit health systems in the area.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: East Houston MOB is a 5-story, 52,131 SF, multi-tenant, medical office building that is currently 82% occupied.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The Property is conveniently located on the Katy Freeway (I-10) just west of Campbell Rd.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Medical Real Estate, Inc., in conjunction with CBRE, Inc., is pleased to exclusively offer for sale an existing medical office building (AOKC Medical Center) and adjacent land (the “Property”) in the heart of the affluent Memorial Villages. The two-story medical office building is 30,036 rentable square feet and fully leased, with lease terms up to 15 years remaining. Both tracts of land are ready for development.  Please go to the Property Website for additional information.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located along Ed Carey Drive and directly across the street from Valley Baptist Medical Center, this office building is an excellent investment with a premiere location.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This medical building consists of two built-out floors equipped with a  fully functional elevator. Previous tenants included Allegian Advantage (HMO) on the first floor, and Valley Baptist on the second floor.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This vacant medical suite has 2 floors facing N. Ed Carey Drive. The first floor consists of 2 large private offices, a large reception desk, and a waiting room. 4 rest rooms are located on the first floor, as well as 6 exam rooms with dressers, a laboratory, a nurse’s station, a storage area and an X-Ray room with a dark room. The second floor offers a convenient suite with a private office, lounge, rest room, 2 closets, and a storage room. An attached ± 360 sq. ft. car port is also included at the rear of this property.
